border-color</strong>\", \"fields.sw-color-danger\": \"Variable: <strong>sw-color-danger</strong>\", \"fields.sw-logo-desktop\": \"Displayed for viewports of above 991px <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>sw-logo-desktop</strong>\", \"fields.sw-logo-favicon\": \"Variable: <strong>sw-logo-favicon</strong>\", \"fields.zen-input-color\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-input-color</strong>\", \"fields.sw-color-success\": \"Variable: <strong>sw-color-success</strong>\", \"fields.sw-color-warning\": \"Variable: <strong>sw-color-warning</strong>\", \"fields.zen-container-bg\": \"Leave the field empty or enter \'transparent\' to make the container backgrounds invisible. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-container-bg</strong>\", \"fields.zen-footer-color\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-footer-color</strong>\", \"fields.zen-header-color\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-header-color</strong>\", \"fields.zen-header-style\": \"With this selection, the representation of the header can be set to a single-line or multi-line header. With a single-line header, the main navigation is shown in one line with the logo and the shop navigation. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-header-style</strong>\", \"fields.zen-layout-style\": \"boxed = Boxed <br> full-width-boxed = Full Width Boxed <br> full-width-header = Full Width Header <br> full-width = Full Width <br><br>Sets the basic layout width of the shop: Boxed = Limited width; Full Width Boxed = elements limited width and backgrounds fit to browser width; FullWidthHeader = Header elements fit to browser edge all other content have a limited width, backgrounds fit to browser edge; FullWidth = elements and backgrounds fit to browser border <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-layout-style</strong>\", \"fields.zen-search-color\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-search-color</strong>\", \"fields.zen-search-style\": \"The search can be displayed in the default (open) or expandable and overlay. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-search-style</strong>\", \"fields.sw-headline-color\": \"Variable: <strong>sw-headline-color</strong>\", \"fields.zen-header-height\": \"in px - Set the height of the main header element for bigger viewports. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-header-height</strong>\", \"fields.zen-layout-bg-img\": \"Background image of the body. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-layout-bg-img</strong>\", \"fields.zen-logo-position\": \"Place the logo inside the header. The other elements such as search and shop navigation are also automatically realigned. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-logo-position</strong>\", \"fields.zen-search-border\": \"If the search appearance is set to <strong>\'Overlay\'</strong>, the border-color is used as underline color. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-search-border</strong>\", \"fields.zen-sticky-header\": \"The header will be stick to the top when you scroll to bottom of the page. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-sticky-header</strong>\", \"fields.zen-top-bar-color\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-top-bar-color</strong>\", \"fields.zen-top-bar-style\": \"In addition to the top bar that can be folded in or out, it can also be displayed as an offcanvas element like the shopping cart. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-top-bar-style</strong>\", \"fields.zen-breadcrumbs-bg\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-breadcrumbs-bg</strong>\", \"fields.zen-category-image\": \"If active, the category picture is inserted as a background in the first section of the set experience world. Categories without a category image represent the background image inserted in the shopping experience as a fallback. <br><br>[‚â°] This option can be individually overwritten in each category. <br><br><br>Variable: <strong>zen-category-image</strong>\", \"fields.zen-input-focus-bg\": \"Variable: <strong>zen-input-focus-bg</strong>\", \"fields.sw-background-color\": \"Variable: <strong>sw-background-color</strong>\", \"fields.sw-color-buy-button\": \"Variable: <strong>sw-color-buy-button</strong>\", \"fields.sw-font-family-base\": \"1. Visit h